{"tid":1466343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷靜呀屌","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:00:37.000Z","uid":15348,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fca41af8edb66b466dad350829d9b11ae783c0f","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsKRrtW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsKRrtW.jpg&h=38b299c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天琦講過 唔好將仇恨帶出嚟<br />\n憤怒係好合理，但唔好俾憤怒支配咗自己呀！<br />\n控制自己，唔好俾自己變成自己最憎最討厭既人 - 以暴易暴既黑警<br />\n<br />\n優先係諗點樣化解今次既危機呀，唔係捉鬼呀<br />\n唔好搞到自己友提心吊膽咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我求下你哋<br />\n唔好重蹈覆轍呀，唔好令雨革既歷史再次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4819e73284ab358fe6028e25319c69fd976c84b","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我求下你哋要冷靜"},{"pid":"f3591c9c4bb474d9e25c96a3444fe6c1b220e39d","tid":1466343,"uid":247227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"機場同地鐵唔同。地鐵不合作可以玩，但機場係用黎文宣 希望外國勢力幫助 唔係令外國勢力憎恨我地！ 唔好再block外國人。 我地要靠外國傳媒幫手。 就快又要全球登廣告，唔好搞衰呢件事。"},{"pid":"23c0dd11f597a9f6b29596a50240c8dfc7bed6c9","tid":1466343,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"雨傘運動輸咗係咁捉鬼 失焦<br />\n辛辛苦苦過去咗嘅兩個月<br />\n傷嘅傷 被捕嘅被捕 失去嘅失去<br />\n唔好再講乜野鬼唔鬼啦<br />\n811 有鬼做示威者開始就知一直都有鬼<br />\n我地做好自己要做嘅野咪得囉<br />\n集中返五大訴求<br />\n818再次上街"},{"pid":"b31a96ff04644d2d39e7f7863bd84a2cbc5f9d3f","tid":1466343,"uid":41875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗主義</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">解散軍</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">大台</span>出沒注意</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登忽然出現大量打手</span><br />\n<br />\n行動有鬼<br />\n=&gt;鬼嘅特徵<br />\n=&gt;掛住捉鬼<br />\n=&gt;互相猜忌<br />\n=&gt;限制行動<br />\n=&gt;出現糾察<br />\n=&gt;話人搞事<br />\n=&gt;分化大眾<br />\n=&gt;大台形成<br />\n<br />\n大家要留意呢排有好多人包括現場人士，議員，KOL限制你地嘅行動，講出似是而非，要保護邊個邊個唔好咁做，呢啲行為完全推翻呢2個月be water，兄弟爬山，不分化不割蓆嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心解散軍。義士們，我相信你地！</span>"},{"pid":"bb51f137b24b1643fb031ecbad9116fb960b5aef","tid":1466343,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"條友仲開記招！ 非法禁固呀家陣, 搵人提佢收皮啦 危險呀"},{"pid":"f93a6d9a7e6ae54c4dfa35c9ac580b23ab8e48cf","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"出邊好多捉鬼post啦<br />\n唔好浪費時間去捉鬼啦<br />\n我哋做好文宣同討論對策啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173155048cf5d0b51331210099e6692b0b9790c5","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"冷靜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87686d17306dde54261a75b857e73e219a7955c4","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"拜託你哋要冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eadf64107300584ccbba4e870901908e3a89b7","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"一個人喺憤怒個陣係最易做錯決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f027dfaac58660a21e97c5002209081a1c2e0b08","tid":1466343,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75eb00e5d6da8e3fc19405e7966931b3fb8bb2b3","tid":1466343,"uid":47028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"小弟想講少少意見，我好清楚可能有人唔啱聽。<br />\n今日堵塞機場唔放人入機，小弟絕對覺得有用。但事實上都係阻到人，人地可以大條道理屌鳩我地。<br />\n係咁既情況希望咁多位巴打唔好情緒發泄在先，大條道理講我地爭取點點點，第一刻對方好多人唔鍾意聽。<br />\n不如大家選擇講聲&ldquo;唔好意思&rdquo;，&ldquo;對唔住&rdquo;，&ldquo;阻到你麻煩晒&rdquo;之類，再慢慢解釋原因。就算解釋完都不滿既就保持沉默，千祈唔好同佢地嘈。點都係我地阻人在先，虛心接受人地既不滿都係一種有禮既表現，記住我地係做俾國際睇，要保持香港人良善既一面，希望多d巴打明白呢點。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位加油，一日救唔返咁多位義士，一日唔可以放棄。<br />\n辛苦晒你地。"},{"pid":"fe7b3d156c51c9d046c15491e04a8ca6bca67446","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bef67c1648ec891b9ffe6c81cd6423e60fcd041","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"每個人都要冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d231e76812c54f595b71a9be21c25df342e25bfd","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"唔好俾自己變成自己最討厭既人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061270ad6584f0eeade4d3298e51c1ccdb81d71e","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"冷靜！"},{"pid":"249e5de767b53985ad37f235b74ec663a06b6f21","tid":1466343,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:32.000Z","msg":"一定要冷靜呀！！"},{"pid":"28132d958746027ad676d33992097f8928317a99","tid":1466343,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b17b4a3456c00e7cea3d0f74b15baae81a7d6d3","tid":1466343,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">請停止任何失敗主義及分化行為</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">善用不推post功能</span><br />